<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Order Success - TIKO</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f9;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .logo-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #ff9900;
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    .header {
      font-size: 28px;
      color: #333333;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .greeting-emoji {
      font-size: 32px;
      margin-left: 10px;
    }

    .success-banner {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      border-left: 4px solid #ff9900;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    }

    .ticket-details {
      background-color: #fff8f0;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 25px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      border: 1px solid #ffe0b2;
    }

    .detail-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin: 10px 0;
      padding: 8px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ffe0b2;
    }

    .detail-row:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .detail-label {
      color: #666;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .detail-value {
      color: #333;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .qr-code-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 2px dashed #ff9900;
    }

    .qr-code-placeholder {
      width: 150px;
      height: 150px;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .important-note {
      background-color: #fff3cd;
      border: 1px solid #ffeeba;
      color: #856404;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .divider {
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #ff9900, transparent);
      margin: 30px 0;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #666666;
      font-size: 14px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    }

    .social-links {
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .social-icon {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 35px;
      height: 35px;
      background-color: #ff9900;
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin: 0 10px;
      line-height: 35px;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .signature {
      font-style: italic;
      color: #888;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="logo-container">
      <span class="logo">TIKO</span>
    </div>

    <h1 class="header">
      Halo, {{username}}
      <span class="greeting-emoji">ðŸ‘‹</span>
    </h1>

    <div class="success-banner">
      <p style="margin: 0;">ðŸŽ‰ Pembelian tiket Anda berhasil!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="ticket-details">
      <div class="detail-row">
        <span class="detail-label">Nama Konser</span>
        <span class="detail-value">{{concertName}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="detail-row">
        <span class="detail-label">Kategori Tiket</span>
        <span class="detail-value">{{categoryName}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="detail-row">
        <span class="detail-label">Tanggal</span>
        <span class="detail-value">{{concertDate}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="detail-row">
        <span class="detail-label">Lokasi</span>
        <span class="detail-value">{{concertLocation}}</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="qr-code-container">
      <div class="qr-code-placeholder">
        QR Code Tiket Anda
      </div>
      <p style="margin: 10px 0 0; font-size: 12px; color: #666;">
        Tunjukkan QR code ini saat memasuki venue
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="important-note">
      <strong>Penting:</strong> Simpan tiket ini baik-baik dan jangan bagikan dengan orang lain untuk menghindari
      penyalahgunaan tiket.
    </div>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <div class="signature">
      Selamat menikmati konser!<br>
      <strong>Tim TIKO</strong> ðŸŽµ
    </div>

    <div class="social-links">
      <a href="#" class="social-icon">f</a>
      <a href="#" class="social-icon">in</a>
      <a href="#" class="social-icon">ig</a>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2024 TIKO. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #888;">
        Email ini dikirim secara otomatis, mohon tidak membalas email ini.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>